Lockable::VerifyWriteAccess() -- EXCLUSIVE LOCK REQUIRED
The requested operation requires that the current thread holds this lockable object's mutex lock exclusive (read/write) access.
To acquire exclusive lock from C++, call Lockable::GetExclusiveLock() and hold the lock via: auto lock(object->GetExclusiveLock()) { ... }
To acquire exclusive lock from C#, call Lockable.GetExclusiveLock() and hold the lock via: using (object.GetExclusiveLock()) { ... }
